function onReceiveNotify(change, value) if (change == "changeValue") then bankNum = self.values["text"]
if (value == "-10") then bankNum = bankNum - 10
if bankNum < 1 then bankNum = 122 + bankNum end elseif (value == "-1") then bankNum = bankNum - 1
if bankNum < 1 then bankNum = 122 + bankNum end elseif (value == "1") then bankNum = bankNum + 1
if bankNum > 122 then bankNum = bankNum - 122 end elseif (value == "10") then bankNum = bankNum + 10
if bankNum > 122 then bankNum = bankNum - 122 end end
self.values["text"] = bankNum end end
